net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.repository

Class DefaultSchemaService

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.repository.base.AbstractSchemaService
      • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.repository.DefaultSchemaService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean

    @Service
 @ConditionalOnProperty(value="net.zethmayr.benjamin.repository.defaultSchemaService")
public class DefaultSchemaService
extends AbstractSchemaService
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
    A default implementation of AbstractSchemaService that
    • binds all repositories,
    • establishes schema for EnumRepository and MapperRepository instances,
    • inserts data for EnumRepository instances,
    and provides methods to collectively truncate and drop repositories.
